        "text": "MiroShark just merged its third language — French, contributed by Zarbel974 in PR #222, touching 32 Vue components with 1,627 tr() calls. The pattern is now proven and frictionless: one dictionary file, zero component changes. Two more languages need to land. Any bilingual developer who has forked the repo (285 of them) can ship a language in a weekend. The market turns \"I could contribute\" into \"I should contribute before someone else claims my language.\"",
